OL,3,CRegulator rules 132% electricity price
OL,4,Chike 'unfair' and promises action
OL,6,FA 132% price hike for electricity in
OL,7,FSark is "neither fair nor reasonable",
OL,8,Fthe island's regulator has concluded.
OL,10,FThe Price Control Commissioner, Shane
OL,11,FLynch, says he intends to set a legal
OL,12,Flimit on what customers can be
OL,13,Fcharged, which will come into force
OL,14,Ffrom midnight on Tuesday 30 September
OL,15,For earlier.
OL,17,FHowever, he has not yet announced what
OL,18,Fthat price cap will be.
