OL,3,CRegulator rules 132% electricity price
OL,4,Chike 'unfair' and promises action
OL,6,FCustomers of Sark Electricity Limited
OL,7,F(SEL), the island's only power
OL,8,Fcompany, were given less than a week's
OL,9,Fnotice of two significant increases,
OL,10,Fwhich saw the cost of a unit jump from
OL,11,F49p to #1.14 on 1 September.
OL,13,FThe utility firm says the rise is
OL,14,Fpartly needed to cover legal costs to
OL,15,Ffight the attempted compulsory
OL,16,Fpurchase by Chief Pleas, but
OL,17,Fgovernment officials have called the
OL,18,Fmove "unjustified".
