OL,3,CRegulator rules 132% electricity price
OL,4,Chike 'unfair' and promises action
OL,6,FBreaking down the unit price, Mr Lynch
OL,7,Fsays the standard 53.6p charge per
OL,8,Fkilowatt-hour for fuel and fixed costs
OL,9,Ftogether does not appear "unfair and
OL,10,Funreasonable".
OL,12,FHowever, he says SEL's decision to add
OL,13,Fa legal levy of 40p and a consultation
OL,14,Flevy of 20p "have, by themselves,
OL,15,Fresulted in an overall unit price
OL,16,Fwhich is neither fair nor reasonable".
OL,18,FThe Commissioner explains that these
OL,19,Ftwo extra charges will see the utility
OL,20,Ffirm generate an extra #70,000 per
OL,21,Fmonth on average.
