OL,3,CRegulator rules 132% electricity price
OL,4,Chike 'unfair' and promises action
OL,6,FMr Lynch says that during his
OL,7,Finvestigation, SEL did not respond to
OL,8,Frequests for information within the
OL,9,Fformal time period and when they did,
OL,10,Fthey did not give the documents
OL,11,Frequired.
OL,13,FHe adds: "On 15 September 2025 (at
OL,14,F16:22), the last day and the last hour
OL,15,Fof the two-week consultation period, I
OL,16,Freceived a letter from advocates
OL,17,Facting on behalf of SEL.
