OL,6,F"The letter stated that SEL would not
OL,7,Fbe engaging further with the purported
OL,8,Fconsultation paper under Section 14
OL,9,Fbecause SEL did not believe that the
OL,10,Fprocess was a lawful one.
OL,12,F"SEL was also offered a two-hour time
OL,13,Fslot (five available times were
OL,14,Foffered) to make verbal
OL,15,Frepresentations on the consultation
OL,16,Fpaper. SEL did not take up this
OL,17,Fopportunity."
